title: How do I delete past searches that have the globe image on the left?
content:
Hello there.

I cannot delete the globe image next to past searches. It seems that you cannot delete them either. I get the error message This is a web page that you've visited before and its related to what you're typing". I tried clearing my browser history, and that does nothing to the globe searches! How do I delete them?

Please respond back. They are very annoying as they keep appearing when I search.
